		''' <summary>
		''' Gets the ParameterDescriptor for each of this MethodDescriptor's
		''' method's parameters.
		''' </summary>
		''' <returns> The locale-independent names of the parameters.  May return
		'''          a null array if the parameter names aren't known. </returns>
